Question: What type of device is made of the same material as the remote the man is to the left of?

Reference Answer: phone

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n526228.jpg

Original program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='man')
IMAGE0=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='remote')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='device')
IMAGE2=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX2)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What material is the remote made of?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE2,question='What material is the device made of?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
